<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN218-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. picirāntaiyār vaṭakkiruntāraik kaṇṭakaṇṇakaṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN218">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>poṉṉun tukiru muttu maṉṉiya</l>
<l>māmalai payanta kāmaru maṇiyu</l>
<l>miṭaipaṭac cēya vāyiṉun toṭaipuṇarn</l>
<l>taruvilai naṉkala mamaikkuṅ kālai</l>
<l>yoruvaḻit tōṉṟiyāṅ keṉṟuñ cāṉṟōr</l>
<l>cāṉṟōr pāla rāpa</l>
<l>cālār cālār pālarā kupavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Although gold, coral, pearls and the desirable </l>
<l>sapphire that was yielded by the lasting big mountain (1f.)</l>
<l corresp="3a-c">were far apart when they appeared in space, </l>
<l corresp="3d-4">at the time when a good ornament of rare price is put together, </l>
<l corresp="5ab">appearing in one way worthy men always </l>
<l corresp="6">are those that have a share in worthy men. </l>
<l corresp="7">Unworthy ones are those that have a share in the unworthy. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
